parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCM can cause the vehicle to shift hard, stall, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the vehicle vibrates or jerks violently
the engine RPMs race or surge
the vehicle rolls away when parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the vehicle vibrates or jerks violently
the engine RPMs race or surge
the vehicle rolls away when parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Parking Issues (Rolling Away or Unintended Movement)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Parking issues can cause the vehicle to roll away or move unintentionally, leading to accidents or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls away when parked
the parking brake fails to engage

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock up or become difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
the vehicle drifts or veers to one side
the steering wheel has a "dead spot" or excessive "free play".

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.
symptoms: passenger airbag sensor is set off
airbag does not deploy in an accident
seatbelt warning lights remain illuminated despite seatbelt being fastened.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A cracked dashboard can lead to airbag deployment issues, potentially causing injury or death in the event of an accident. Additionally, the cracked dashboard can create a distraction for the driver, increasing the risk of an accident.
symptoms: cracked dashboard above the center of the passenger side airbag
cracked dashboard adjacent to the airbag cover.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can lead to the airbag not deploying in an accident, potentially causing injury or death.
symptoms: Passenger airbag sensor is set off
airbag does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking of the dashboard can lead to a safety hazard in the event of an airbag deployment, potentially causing injury to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: particularly around the passenger airbag area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Leaks in the exhaust system can cause carbon monoxide poisoning, and broken exhaust manifold bolts can lead to engine damage and decreased performance.
Engine stalling can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially when occurring at high speeds.
Rust on the frame can lead to structural damage, compromising the vehicle's safety and integrity.
Failure of the transmission and braking systems can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: brake light and ABS light coming on
